      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a76df5fa-d26f-11e3-a9d1-52540035b04c).  Ran 4 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
