      "date": "2014-05-27 18:58:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nNote that I don't think the fix in liblustreapi.c in Patch #1 was bad to have.  It fixes the problem of an application wanting a volatile file on a non-Lustre filesystem, which is not a bad thing, but it doesn't fix the problem of unlinking volatile files on a Lustre filesystem.",
